Package etomica.data

Class DataPumpListenerPowStrict

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataProcessor
      • etomica.data.DataPump
        • etomica.data.DataPumpListenerPowStrict
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAction, DataPipe, IDataSink, IntegratorListener

    public class DataPumpListenerPowStrict
extends DataPump
implements IntegratorListener
    DataPump class that takes data at steps pow^i, i=0,1,2,3... This can be used to take (and retain) data over many orders of magnitude. Pow is 2 by default.
